div.p: Level Up Academy is a proud member of the Summit Learning Platform.
Please read this importantmessage from our Director

span.span: In a Personalized Learning experience, students are aware of what they are learning, why they are learning, and how they learn best. They become self-directed learners and develop the behaviors and mindsets for success. Our emphasis on personalized learning allows teachers to honor where each child is in their development and to guide them to mastery at their own pace. Our students will continually "LEVEL UP." This differs from the calendar and age driven model of social promotion. By tapping into the intrinsic motivation and curiosity of every child, we deliver higher than usual growth.
